locate where API key is sourced, add better error messaging and health check tool (openplanner_health).\\n5) Update README to describe skill workflows and show examples.\\n\\nConstraints:\\n- Keep tool names underscore-style.\\n- Prefer apply_patch for edits.\\n- Add minimal tests or at least a manual verification checklist.\\n\\nReturn:\\n- file list, changelog, verification steps.\"}},\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":1}","headers":{"host":"err-stealth-16-ai-studio-a1vgg.tailbe888a.ts.net","user-agent":"openai-mcp/1.0.0","content-length":"2096","accept":"application/json, text/event-stream","accept-encoding":"gzip, deflate, br, zstd","authorization":"[REDACTED]","content-type":"application/json","mcp-protocol-version":"2025-06-18","mcp-session-id":"b8bbe34a-4e6b-435d-8a1f-b1dad6548f43","tailscale-funnel-request":"?1","traceparent":"00-6989907b0000000091e02ea9bda80e37-e9b3808a114ce811-00","tracestate":"dd=s:-1;p:7bee66721c7389c8;t.dm:-3","x-datadog-parent-id":"18332017996598127586","x-datadog-sampling-priority":"-1","x-datadog-tags":"_dd.p.tid=6989907b00000000,_dd.p.dm=-3","x-datadog-trace-id":"10511452836848995895","x-forwarded-for":"52.255.111.30","x-forwarded-host":"err-stealth-16-ai-studio-a1vgg.tailbe888a.ts.net","x-forwarded-proto":"https","x-openai-session":"v1/4qFqj35bJpD44kMwoHzx2cDg1iCypjDQm7UMcmIwhqf35NpiWC84jOc91X8zcbIwRfpkNuEilULl","x-openai-subject":"v1/EoL8uJNwuHvN3hSuCC9BvtYvBPjCdVdLp6PTYPGDOQt8z4LENEQfcU"},"msg":"proxying to MCP"}
